      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including professional subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, while the limited-slip differential ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. Equipped with a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers, the turn-in remains precise. Though the finish shows minor road-wear typical of a dedicated driver's car",
